FILE MANAGEMENT STRUCTURE

roject/
├── data/
│   ├── raw/                   # source docs (pdf, txt, md)
│   ├── processed/             # cleaned & chunked text
│   └── metadata.json          # doc IDs, source tracking
│
├── src/                        # everything the SERVER owns
│   ├── server.js               # entry point — starts Express, mounts routes
│   │
│   ├── routes/
│   │   └── query.js            # POST /api/query → retrieve + generate + respond
│   │
│   ├── ingestion/
│   │   ├── loadDocs.js         # reads files from data/raw
│   │   ├── chunkText.js        # splits into overlapping chunks
│   │   └── embedAndStore.js    # generates embeddings → vector store
│   │
│   ├── vectorstore/
│   │   └── store.js            # connects to Chroma/Pinecone/Firestore
│   │
│   ├── retrieval/
│   │   └── retriever.js        # similarity search (top-k chunks)
│   │
│   └── generation/
│       ├── promptTemplate.js   # builds final prompt w/ retrieved context
│       └── llmClient.js        # calls Groq/Claude API
│
├── public/                     # everything the BROWSER owns, served via express.static()
│   ├── index.html
│   ├── style.css
│   ├── chat.js                 # fetch() calls to /api/query — no API keys here, ever
│   └── assets/
│       ├── fonts/
│       │   ├── Inter-Regular.woff2
│       │   └── Inter-Bold.woff2
│       └── images/
│           ├── logo.svg
│           ├── favicon.ico
│           └── bg-pattern.png
│
├── scripts/
│   └── buildIndex.js           # run once (or on doc updates): ingest → populate vector store
│
├── .env                         # API keys, vector DB config — used ONLY inside src/
├── .gitignore
├── package.json
└── README.md
